===Etymology 1===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*kʷ-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|why}}, from {{inh|en|ang|hwȳ|t=why}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*hwī|t=by what, how}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*kʷey}}, instrumental case of {{m|ine-pro|*kʷis|t=who}}, {{m|ine-pro|*kʷid|t=what}}.

Cognate with {{cog|osx|hwī|t=why}}, {{m|osx|hwiu|t=how; why}}, {{cog|gmh|wiu||how, why}}, archaic {{cog|da|-}} and {{cog|nb|-}} {{m|da|hvi||why}}, {{cog|nn|kvi||why}}, {{cog|sv|vi||why}}, {{cog|fo|-}} and {{cog|is|-}} {{m|fo|hví||why}}, {{cog|la|quī||why}}, {{cog|grc|πεῖ||where}}. Compare {{cog|ang|þȳ||because, since, on that account, therefore, then|lit=by that, for that}}. See {{l|en|thy}}.

